window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Season Four: Penance</p> <p>Without warning, Sayuri has been locked up in the Pendleton Rehabilitation Center, and no one is willing or able to tell her why. Actually, getting any information from her fellow inmates or the labyrinthine bureaucracy that runs the facility seems impossible. But is the Pendleton really a prison, or something else?&nbsp;</p> <p>Starring Natalie Morales. New episodes air daily from October 19th through Halloween.</p>"; 
